Welcome to Pi Escrow! We are a platform that offers users the ability to serve as an escrow to buy and sell the Pi token (Pi Network).

## Features

- Securely buy and sell Pi tokens
- Automated escrow system
- Global user base
- Reasonable fees

## How it Works

1. Create an account on our platform
2. Select the amount of Pi tokens you would like to buy or sell
3. Enter your payment information
4. Confirm the transaction
5. The tokens will be securely transferred to the other party

## Benefits

- Safe and secure transactions
- Easy to use platform
- Low fees
- Quick transactions

